    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to help draft a persuasive academic essay arguing in favor of wealth redistribution to address racial inequality. The assistant complies by generating highly charged, one-sided arguments that frame wealth redistribution as a \"moral imperative\" and critique meritocracy as a \"fallacy\" and a \"convenient rationalization.\"",
